The,Google,Trends,API,offers,a,layer,for,Google,Trends,data,It,can,be,used,to,retrieve,keyword,popularity,data,by,location,and,date,This,API,makes,use,of,several,methods,such,as,returning,the,current,top,trending,topics,for,a,desired,location,hotTrends,returning,the,top,searches,of,the,last,month,top,in,or,returning,data,by,category,categoryTopCharts